README FOR CS275 LAB5

This lab requires the node.js use thats why we have to iniate the server and from our terminal and then go to localhost:8080 for the index html.
Then using the dropdown menu we choose what kind of table we want to see, which those tables are connected to mysql database.
I created the database by using these commands;
1)CREATE TABLE STUDENT (
    id varchar(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    firstname varchar(255),
    lastname varchar(255) NOT NULL,
    dob DATETIME NOT NULL,
    major varchar(255),
    PRIMARY KEY (id)
); 
2)CREATE TABLE COURSE (
    id varchar(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    description varchar(255) NOT NULL
); 
3)CREATE TABLE GRADES (
    courseid varchar(255) NOT NULL,
    studentid varchar(255) NOT NULL,
    term varchar(255) NOT NULL,
    grade varchar(1) NOT NULL
); 

There is a attached image in the same folder which shows the table context, if needed please check that picture.

